      "id": "1833625321775436208",
      "text": "🇺🇸JD VANCE: WE TRADED DICK CHENEY FOR BOBBY KENNEDY\n\nDavid Sacks:\n\n“On a separate track, a few weeks ago, we had Bobby Kennedy endorse Donald Trump. \n\nSo, you now have a dynamic where the Bush Republicans are now Harris Democrats, and the Kennedy Democrats are now Trump Republicans. \n\nClearly, something big is happening in our politics here. \n\nCan you explain this realignment?\n\nHow do you see it?”\n\nJ.D. Vance:\n\nOne way to think about it is that we traded Dick Cheney for Bobby Kennedy, and that's an upgrade I'll take every single day of the week, right? \n\nI mean, one way of understanding it is you have to ask yourself who has benefited and who has been harmed over the last 30 years of the bipartisan consensus in this country?”\n\nSource: @JDVance, @theallinpod, @DavidSacks",
